articles.title: Mortgage rates drop to lowest since early February 2023 after Fed’s jumbo interest rate cut - CNN
articles.description: Mortgage rates continued to decline this week, taking a little more pressure off America’s tight housing market as the Federal Reserve ramps up its efforts to keep the economy on an even keel.
